answers.answer: I feel you. My due date was yesterday. I was checked on the 8th and I'm not dilated and my cervix is still high. Luckily I don't think they will let me go to much longer since I've had preeclampsia with both my previous pregnancies and my blood pressure was high at my last appointment.

Iv no had any thing to make then want to get me going. I'm just getting really fed up and I'm so emotional I lost my dad last year 4 days after I found out I was pregnant ever things getting to me I'm finding it so hard just want to feel normal again hope u r baby's here soon xxx
